<lb n="0732c15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="w"><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pJ29p0732c1501">　　　<note n="0732c1501" resp="CBETA" type="add">四川向化侯養元譚公諱詣捐【CB】，<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>【嘉興】</note><app n="0732c1501"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">四川向化侯養元譚公諱詣捐</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】"><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear></rdg></app>俸刊</p></cb:div>
